  "page": "Feastfires",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Westerlands.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The westerlands and the location of Feastfires\"><img alt=\"The westerlands and the location of Feastfires\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7f/The_Westerlands.png/400px-The_Westerlands.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"444\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7f/The_Westerlands.png/600px-The_Westerlands.png 1.5x, /images/7/7f/The_Westerlands.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 58.3%; left: 5.6%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 10px; font-size: 10px;\"><img alt=\"The westerlands and the location of Feastfires\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Feastfires\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/15px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/20px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 100%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Feastfires</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> and the location of Feastfires\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Feastfires</b> is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Prester\" title=\"House Prester\">House Prester</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>. It is located at the southwestern tip of a peninsula in the <a href=\"/index.php/Sunset_Sea\" title=\"Sunset Sea\">Sunset Sea</a>. The peninsula is west of <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a> and south of <a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a>. Feastfires is southwest of nearby <a href=\"/index.php/Kayce\" title=\"Kayce\">Kayce</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Feastfires&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Lord of the Iron Islands\">Lord of the Iron Islands</a>, occupied <a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>, so Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Johanna_Lannister\" title=\"Johanna Lannister\">Johanna Lannister</a> gathered a small fleet of cogs and fishing boats beneath the walls of Feastfires. <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">Ironborn</a> longships <a href=\"/index.php/Ambush_at_Fair_Isle\" title=\"Ambush at Fair Isle\">ambushed the westermen</a> when they sailed to retake Fair Isle, however, and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Prester\" title=\"House Prester\">Prester</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarbeck\" title=\"House Tarbeck\">Tarbeck</a>, and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Erwin_Lannister\" title=\"Erwin Lannister\">Erwin Lannister</a> were killed. <sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Dalton gathered longships to Feastfires and other ports to await the fleet of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn Velaryon</a>, but the Red Kraken was assassinated at <a href=\"/index.php/Faircastle\" title=\"Faircastle\">Faircastle</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a> before the Oakenfist arrived in the west.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>According to a semi-canon source,<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister_(son_of_Gerold)\" title=\"Jason Lannister (son of Gerold)\">Jason Lannister</a> resided at Feastfires after marrying Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Marla_Prester\" title=\"Marla Prester\">Marla Prester</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Feastfires&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Map_of_the_South\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Map of the South\">Map of the South</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - War and Peace and Cattle Shows.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - The Voyage of Alyn Oakenfist.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">georgerrmartin.com: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.georgerrmartin.com/world-of-ice-and-fire-sample/\">WORLD OF ICE AND FIRE SAMPLE</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Region_Westerlands\" title=\"Template:Region Westerlands\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Region_Westerlands&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Region Westerlands (page does not